<plot>Oil Can Harry captures Fanny and throws her into a cellar full of barely caged lions. However, over the next few months, Fanny has befriended the lions and other animals, and when Harry checks up on her, is playing cards with them. She gets the animals to attack Harry and, ultimately, lock him into a room. Meanwhile, Strongheart's dog has located Fanny and brings Strongheart to the rescue.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?189240</url></doc>
